        Adds a ManagedFunctionTypeBuilder to this FunctionNamespaceBuilder definition.
        Specified by:
        addManagedFunctionType in interface FunctionNamespaceBuilder
        Type Parameters:
        M - Dependency key type.
        F - Flow key type.
        Parameters:
        taskName - Name of the ManagedFunction.
        objectKeysClass - Enum providing the keys of the dependent Object instances required by the ManagedFunctionTypeBuilder. This may be null if the ManagedFunctionTypeBuilder requires no dependent Object instances or they are Indexed.
        flowKeysClass - Enum providing the keys of the Flow instigated by the ManagedFunctionTypeBuilder. This may be null if the ManagedFunctionTypeBuilder does not instigate Flow instances or they are Indexed.
        Returns:
        ManagedFunctionTypeBuilder to provide type definition of the added ManagedFunction.
